Package: rayfocus
Type: Package
Title: Render Depth of Field for Images
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-10-19
Author: Tyler Morgan-Wall
Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: Uses a depth map to render depth of field for an image. Supports variable camera settings and custom aperture shapes.
License: GPL-3
